# Contact form (Formspree)
# 1. Sign up at https://formspree.io using suminmhrzn18@gmail.com
# 2. Create a new form — Formspree gives you an endpoint like
#    https://formspree.io/f/abcdwxyz  (the part after /f/ is your ID)
# 3. Copy this file to `.env` and paste the ID below, then restart `npm run dev`.
VITE_FORMSPREE_ID=YOUR_FORM_ID
